OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,FMartyn Hammond speaks to ITV West
OL,7,FCountry about his 40-year battle for
OL,8,Fan apology after being dismissed from
OL,9,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,11,FA Navy veteran who says he was
OL,12,Farrested, detained and thrown out of
OL,13,Fthe military for being gay has
OL,14,Freceived an official apology almost 40
OL,15,Fyears later.
OL,17,FMartyn Hammond joined the Royal Navy
OL,18,Fin 1981 at the age of 17, when being
OL,19,Fgay in the armed forces was forbidden.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
