OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,FFive years later, after serving in
OL,7,FCornwall and Hampshire as a Navy cook,
OL,8,FMartyn's sexuality was exposed.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country at
OL,11,Fhis home in Plymouth, Martyn said: "I
OL,12,Fwas good at my job. Very good at my
OL,13,Fjob. I had an exemplary record.
OL,15,F"I kept my private life very private,
OL,16,FI didn't involve it in my work at all.
OL,17,FBut the military police came to arrest
OL,18,Fme.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
