OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1732793268
OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,F"Your whole life is going to implode.
OL,7,FThe Navy was my life at the time and
OL,8,Fthat was about to be ripped away from
OL,9,Fme. I lost my pension, I lost my
OL,10,Fdignity. I went through a lot of
OL,11,Fmental health stress.
OL,13,F"I still do struggle with it, I do get
OL,14,Fincredibly emotional about it because
OL,15,Fit was my life, and to think they
OL,16,Fcould just throw somebody away like
OL,17,Fthat and treat somebody like that -
OL,18,Fyeah, devastating really."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
