OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,FLast year, a review found that
OL,7,Ftreatment of LGBT personnel and
OL,8,Fveterans in the Armed Forces was
OL,9,F'completely unacceptable' and 'highly
OL,10,Fregrettable'.
OL,12,FLord Etherton's report found that
OL,13,Finvestigations in an individual's
OL,14,Fsexuality were intrusive, invasive,
OL,15,Fand for some caused long-lasting and
OL,16,Fsevere impacts to the lives of
OL,17,Fveterans and their families.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
