OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,FThen Prime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,7,Fdescribed the ban, which was lifted in
OL,8,Fthe year 2000, as an "appalling
OL,9,Ffailure".
OL,11,FThis week, Martyn finally received a
OL,12,Fpersonal letter of apology and a
OL,13,Fspecially-made badge.J"It means that
OL,14,Fthe government realises now that this
OL,15,Fshouldn't have happened," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
