OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1732793268
OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,F"There's a lot of people who aren't
OL,7,Fhere today who were kicked out of the
OL,8,Fmilitary. Some people have taken their
OL,9,Flives. People have lost pensions,
OL,10,Fstruggled financially, struggled with
OL,11,Fmental health.
OL,13,F"So the fact it's now been
OL,14,Facknowledged properly, it's a start,
OL,15,Fit's a start to try to make amends a
OL,16,Flittle bit really."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
