OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,FMartyn, who is now 60, is also
OL,7,Fplanning to apply for compensation.
OL,8,FBut he says no amount of money will
OL,9,Fmake up for what he went through.
OL,10,F"It's always made me feel not good
OL,11,Fenough," he said.
OL,13,F"Being gay in the Navy, you're
OL,14,Fconstantly looking over your shoulder.
OL,15,FYou did your best, you did your job,
OL,16,Fyou did what everybody asked. But you
OL,17,Falways felt that because you couldn't
OL,18,Fbe you, you never felt good enough.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
