OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1732793268
OL,3,CNavy veteran arrested for being gay
OL,4,Cgets apology almost 40 years later
OL,6,F"Even now, I've always struggled with
OL,7,Fjobs. I feel I've just had to work
OL,8,Fthat much harder in anything I've
OL,9,Fdone. And I've carried that all my
OL,10,Flife."
OL,12,FMartyn's MP Luke Pollard, who is
OL,13,Fhimself gay and was recently appointed
OL,14,Fas Armed Forces minister, says the
OL,15,Fapology is an important step forward.
OL,17,FThe Government will open a scheme
OL,18,Fallowing people to apply for
OL,19,Fcompensation in January.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
